comments: Mobley (CLE) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly awarded to the Raptors.
Mitchell (CLE) dislodges the ball out of bounds. Play resumes with the Raptors retaining possession.
Poeltl (TOR) brings his hands toward Garland (CLE) and marginal contact occurs as Poeltl releases away to roll.
Allen (CLE) brings his right hand toward Schroder's (TOR) arm and marginal contact occurs after the release of his driving shot attempt.
Garland (CLE) extends his right forearm and initiates contact with Schroder's (TOR) side which affects his SQBR during the drive.
Barnes (TOR) initiates contact with Allen (CLE) as he wraps his left arm around him which affects his FOM as the pick is set.
Barnes (TOR) brings his left forearm toward Garland's (CLE) path and marginal contact occurs during Garland's drive.
Garland (CLE) goes to, not through, Barnes's (TOR) space and marginal contact occurs as Garland releases away at the start of the drive.
Allen (CLE) firms up onto his left leg and does not deliver illegal contact to Barnes' (TOR) during the pick.
Barnes (TOR) moves alongside Garland's (CLE) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Barnes (TOR) goes to, not through, Strus's (CLE) space and marginal contact occurs after he releases the pass at the end of his drive.
Mobley (CLE) releases the inbound pass before the five-second count.
Flynn (TOR) extends both hands forward and initiates contact with Mitchell (CLE) during the drive, affecting his SQBR.
Trent Jr. (TOR) steps out of bounds before starting his upward shooting motion. The possession is correctly awarded to the Cavaliers.
